<div class="container py-5">
  <div class="rv-section-head">
    <h1 class="rv-gradient-text">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    <hr class="rv-rule">
    <p class="rv-sub">Answers for artists, makers, and fans using Red Village in Zimbabwe.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-lg-8">
      <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">
        <div class="accordion-item mb-2 border-0 shadow-sm rounded overflow-hidden">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq1">
            <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapse1">
              How do I open a store on Red Village?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapse1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="faq1" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Create a free account, then open a storefront inside one of our malls. You can list
              products, tracks, and artwork, and manage everything from your dashboard.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item mb-2 border-0 shadow-sm rounded overflow-hidden">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq2">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2">
              Who can sell on the marketplace?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapse2" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq2" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Any verified Zimbabwean creator — DJs, visual artists, photographers, videographers,
              designers, curators, and editors — can run a store and list their work.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item mb-2 border-0 shadow-sm rounded overflow-hidden">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq3">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse3">
              How do events and tickets work?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapse3" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq3" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Organisers publish events on the calendar and sell tickets through the platform. Fans
              browse the <a href="/schedule">schedule</a> and buy tickets directly from the event page.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item mb-2 border-0 shadow-sm rounded overflow-hidden">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq4">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse4">
              What does it cost to join?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapse4" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq4" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Setting up a creator profile and store is free. A small platform fee applies on completed
              sales to keep Red Village running.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item mb-2 border-0 shadow-sm rounded overflow-hidden">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq5">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse5">
              Is my content protected?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapse5" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq5" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              You retain full ownership of your work. Red Village only hosts and promotes it; you control
              your store, pricing, and public profile.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="accordion-item border-0 shadow-sm rounded overflow-hidden">
          <h2 class="accordion-header" id="faq6">
            <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse6" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse6">
              How do I get help?
            </button>
          </h2>
          <div id="collapse6" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="faq6" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-body">
              Reach the team through the <a href="/contact_us">contact page</a>, or email
              <a href="mailto:hello@redvillage.co.zw">hello@redvillage.co.zw</a> and we'll get back to you.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
